1
00:00:22,680 --> 00:00:24,400
I've been looking for you for two years.

2
00:00:24,760 --> 00:00:25,440
My son,

3
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:29,760
I know I was wrong.

4
00:00:31,360 --> 00:00:33,000
I shouldn't have been fooled by a woman.

5
00:00:36,280 --> 00:00:38,440
Can't you be a bit more assertive?

6
00:00:40,840 --> 00:00:41,640
Father,

7
00:00:42,560 --> 00:00:44,280
I've been gradually reclaiming the distribution channels

8
00:00:45,200 --> 00:00:47,160
of the Obedience Water for you over the past few years.

9
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:49,880
I am your most loyal son.

10
00:00:53,920 --> 00:00:55,240
Now,

11
00:00:55,720 --> 00:00:58,240
I only believe in human weaknesses.

12
00:00:58,560 --> 00:00:59,320
Father,

13
00:01:00,160 --> 00:01:01,200
I'm ready.

14
00:01:13,880 --> 00:01:14,640
Good.

15
00:01:38,360 --> 00:01:39,360
Thank you, father.

16
00:01:40,320 --> 00:01:41,280
This means

17
00:01:42,720 --> 00:01:44,440
I've finally gained your approval.

18
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,880
If that's the case,

19
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:54,280
I'll give you a task.

20
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:57,160
Kill Pang Jingfu yourself.

21
00:01:57,880 --> 00:01:58,600
Yes.

22
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,240
Chief Minister Fan,

23
00:02:13,320 --> 00:02:13,960
If you do this,

24
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,080
Ruoyun will be heartbroken.

25
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,440
I've made her heartbroken

26
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:23,680
many times.

27
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:26,320
Shouldn't one be quick to seek revenge

28
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:29,320
against the person they hate the most?

29
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:32,760
Am I right?

30
00:02:34,640 --> 00:02:35,360
Afu,

31
00:02:54,640 --> 00:02:56,000
the jammer has been destroyed.

32
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:56,720
Leave now!

33
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,200
Senior Brother, quickly locate it.

34
00:02:59,200 --> 00:02:59,920
Send someone over.

35
00:03:08,880 --> 00:03:09,800
Professor Bovis,

36
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:11,360
regarding the collaborative project between you and the university

37
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:14,280
on the charity research of nerve repair and behavior correction,

38
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,640
it is said to have helped many

39
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:17,200
patients with post-traumatic stress disorder.

40
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,320
Yes.

41
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:18,960
That's right.

42
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:20,520
Our goal is to utilize

43
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,960
the most cutting-edge medical and psychological methods

44
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:24,120
to help those

45
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,720
who are in behavioral difficulties

46
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,280
and ignored by society

47
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:28,400
to start a new life.

48
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,680
Academic research

49
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,840
should serve people.

50
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:34,840
Professor,

51
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:39,360
I have a few questions

52
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,320
about your research.

53
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:46,000
Dad,

54
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:48,600
I've been gradually taking back

55
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:51,440
the distribution channels of obedience water.

56
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:53,920
I'm your most loyal son.

57
00:03:54,320 --> 00:03:55,240
Now,

58
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:58,600
I only believe in human weaknesses.

59
00:03:58,600 --> 00:03:59,400
Thank you, father.

60
00:04:00,200 --> 00:04:01,080
It means

61
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:02,840
I finally got your approval.

62
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:05,080
If that's the case,

63
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:06,920
I'll give you a task.

64
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:09,200
Kill Pang Jingfu yourself.

65
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:13,600
You...

66
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:15,200
You are Pang Zhengsong who escaped back then.

67
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:16,920
Wanted criminal Pang Zhengsong.

68
00:04:20,840 --> 00:04:21,880
It's a misunderstanding.

69
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:25,160
Hello.

70
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:26,960
Can you explain what that recording means?

71
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:27,720
Hello.

72
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:30,440
Sir.

73
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,080
You...

74
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:51,400
Why bother?

75
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:55,040
Am I not a loser now?

76
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:56,240
Father.

77
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:04,040
Ruoyun.

78
00:06:06,440 --> 00:06:08,160
Don't be afraid.

79
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:50,000
How does it feel to be

80
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,080
a scapegoat?

81
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:23,480
Just like your mother.

82
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:25,920
Be a good scapegoat.

83
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:33,680
This is your fate.

84
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:17,600
No way.

85
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:21,040
My medicine.

86
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,440
My medicine.

87
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:27,560
How could it be?

88
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,000
This time,

89
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:51,720
I didn't go easy.

90
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:08,160
Why do you keep looking into my eyes?

91
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:09,680
Your eyes

92
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:10,720
are beautiful.

93
00:09:11,280 --> 00:09:12,520
I like them.

94
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:22,080
Why did you save me?

95
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:23,400
Pang Jingfu,

96
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:25,240
why?

97
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:27,200
Because I'm worried about you.

98
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:30,000
I made my girlfriend cry.

99
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:31,240
I haven't made up with her yet.

100
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:33,960
Pang Jingfu,

101
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,760
your heartbeat

102
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:36,840
is fast.

103
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:38,840
Because I'm into you.

104
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:41,520
Pang Jingfu,

105
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:42,520
if...

106
00:09:43,400 --> 00:09:44,800
if, I mean, if,

107
00:09:44,800 --> 00:09:45,720
if you have anything

108
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,840
to say to me,

109
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:49,000
you can say it now.

110
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:50,360
Tian Yan,

111
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,880
will you marry me?

112
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,800
I can't sleep.

113
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,560
I want to read a book.

114
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,720
If you just want a book,

115
00:10:06,280 --> 00:10:07,240
why are you hiding?

116
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:16,200
Maybe

117
00:10:16,920 --> 00:10:18,960
I'm born to be your soulmate.

118
00:10:21,680 --> 00:10:23,400
My favorite line is...

119
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:37,840
This one.

120
00:10:40,880 --> 00:10:41,920
I knew you.

121
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:44,240
I'll always remember you.

122
00:10:45,160 --> 00:10:45,680
You were

123
00:10:45,680 --> 00:10:46,960
young then.

124
00:10:47,760 --> 00:10:49,440
Everyone said you were beautiful.

125
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:51,600
Now,

126
00:10:52,560 --> 00:10:54,080
I'm here to tell you,

127
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:57,480
To me,

128
00:10:58,920 --> 00:10:59,800
I think

129
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:02,880
you are more beautiful now than then.

130
00:11:04,520 --> 00:11:05,320
At that time,

131
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:07,120
you were a young woman.

132
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:09,840
Compared to your face at that time,

133
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,080
I love more

134
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:13,800
your face now

135
00:11:13,800 --> 00:11:15,640
that is ravaged by time.
